{"tid":1393970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［水泉澳支那人］打風嗌外賣等逾句鐘 食客揚言投訴外賣員至失業","createTime":"2019-08-01T09:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T07:26:48.000Z","uid":153151,"like":25,"dislike":610,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"3a707feb21b99bd856f880cf4c6546840fba3b53","tid":1393970,"uid":153151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O350adm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO350adm.jpg&h=288476ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食客揚言投訴外賣員至失業。網上圖片<br />\n不少港人喜歡叫外賣，省回排隊時間以及避免日曬雨淋。本港昨午起懸掛八號風球，多處出現狂風暴雨，期間有市民叫連鎖快餐店外賣，但等了超過一小時仍未送達，聲稱要把他投訴至失業。<br />\n<br />\n有網民在Facebook群組「水泉澳邨～水仔是我家」以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簡體字</span></strong></span>發文，指在連鎖快餐店叫外賣後，逾一小時仍未送達，斥「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港的服務水平不及內地！已經投訴那個外賣仔，等待失業吧！廢青</strong></span></span>」。他今日再度發貼指，興奮指已獲該連鎖快餐店回覆：「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">那個卑鄙的外賣仔已經被解僱，終身不得錄用，活該</span></span>」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都認為該食客過火，「打風仲叫外賣，人地途中死咗/受傷邊個揹黑鍋？」、「警察都要39分鐘，外賣1小時很平常的，親！」。亦有網民質疑外賣員被解僱的可信性，「吹水唔抹嘴咁款！邊有咁快會回復啊！最少都等幾日啦！如果有咁快服務就好了」、「原來佢唔知送外賣嘅自僱嘅」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1557616/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-Kelly-Online-%E6%89%93%E9%A2%A8%E5%97%8C%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E7%AD%89%E9%80%BE%E5%8F%A5%E9%90%98-%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E5%93%A1%E8%87%B3%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1557616%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%2597%258C%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E7%25AD%2589%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258F%25A5%25E9%2590%2598-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25A8%2580%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl54oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=3a4a8afd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1557616%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%2597%258C%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E7%25AD%2589%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258F%25A5%25E9%2590%2598-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25A8%2580%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD&h=db1b4319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1557616/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-Kelly-Online-%E6%89%93%E9%A2%A8%E5%97%8C%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E7%AD%89%E9%80%BE%E5%8F%A5%E9%90%98-%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%A3%E5%93%A1%E8%87%B3%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1081000165336471/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1081000165336471%2F&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl54oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=aac26395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1081000165336471/</a>"},{"pid":"92a264fd18004fc7c92ebdbf232314cb6525ea55","tid":1393970,"uid":153151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf1a7ce475acf5a6c05ebea16ebb5e93c92123b","tid":1393970,"uid":102609,"like":358,"dislike":1,"score":357,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:17:05.000Z","msg":"一打開睇<br />\n個水泉澳fb grp簡介已經係殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94276746052eeb02a5f9d95cb111f056bbecc1b6","tid":1393970,"uid":283157,"like":218,"dislike":7,"score":211,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:17:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9f2e63e44f7e6715da